{
  "id": "60ab9fa6c22de9001c5c70c4",
  "title": "耐戦略性の定義",
  "created": 1621860263,
  "updated": 1622179827,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6c22de9001c5c70c4",
      "text": "耐戦略性の定義",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9faeaff09e00001741c9",
      "text": "[耐戦略性]の定義 from [メカニズムデザイン(書籍)]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860271,
      "updated": 1621860272
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e0000174194",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860270
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e0000174196",
      "text": "基礎概念",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e0000174197",
      "text": "個人の集合[$ I = \\{1, 2, \\ldots, n \\} ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e0000174198",
      "text": "[帰結]の集合[$ X]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e0000174199",
      "text": "　多くの場合、実行可能な資源配分の集合",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e000017419a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e000017419b",
      "text": "選好:[$ \\succsim]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e000017419c",
      "text": " 選好はもっぱら個人iの選好[$ \\succsim_i]の形で使われるが定義に際してはiは関係ないので添字を省いた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e000017419d",
      "text": " 3つの条件を満たすX上の二項関係",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e000017419e",
      "text": " \t[反射性][$ \\forall x \\in X, x \\succsim x ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e000017419f",
      "text": " \t[推移性][$ \\forall x, y, z \\in X, x \\succsim y \\wedge y \\succsim z \\Rightarrow x \\succsim z]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741a0",
      "text": " 　[完備性]\t[$ \\forall x, y \\in X, x \\succsim y \\vee y \\succsim x]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741a1",
      "text": "　関連 [順序集合]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741a2",
      "text": "　　要するに選好とは[全順序]から[反対称律](xがy以上でyがx以上ならx=yである)がなくなったもの",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741a3",
      "text": "　　[前順序]に[完備性]を付け加えた物",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741a4",
      "text": "　　\t>通常、経済学やゲーム理論では選好は前順序であると仮定する - [ゲーム理論〔第3版〕]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741a5",
      "text": "　選好の対象部分",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741a6",
      "text": " [$ \\forall x,y \\in X, x \\sim y \\Leftrightarrow x \\succsim y \\wedge y \\succsim x]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741a7",
      "text": "　選好の非対称部分",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741a8",
      "text": " [$ \\forall x,y \\in X, x \\succ y \\Leftrightarrow x \\succsim y \\wedge y \\not\\succsim x]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741a9",
      "text": "　選考の非対称性",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741aa",
      "text": "\t[$ \\forall x,y \\in X, x \\sim y \\Leftrightarrow x = y]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741ab",
      "text": "\t　相異なる2要素が同程度に好まれることはない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741ac",
      "text": "\t　こういう選好を「強選好」と呼ぶ(線形選好と呼ぶ人もいるがこの本では誤解を避けて使わない)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741ad",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741ae",
      "text": "X上の選好すべての集合[$ \\mathscr{R} ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741af",
      "text": "個人iが取りうる選好[$ \\mathscr{D}_i \\subseteq \\mathscr{R} ]を選好集合と呼ぶ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741b0",
      "text": "　個人によって異なりうる定式化になってるが、具体的な問題によってはもちろん同一にもなりうる。例えば3人の候補者から1人選ぶ投票を考える時は各個人の取りうる選好は当然同一である",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741b1",
      "text": "個人iの選好: [$ \\succsim_i \\in \\mathscr{D}_i]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741b2",
      "text": "　二項関係が「二項関係の集合」の要素なだけだが、脳内でパースエラーを起こしそうだ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741b3",
      "text": "　[$ X]上の二項関係Rは、そもそも順序対[$ X^2]の部分集合に過ぎない: [$ x R y \\Leftrightarrow (x, y) \\in R]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741b4",
      "text": "ドメイン: [$ \\mathscr{D}_I \\equiv \\mathscr{D}_1 \\times \\mathscr{D}_2 \\times \\cdots \\times \\mathscr{D}_n]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741b5",
      "text": "選好組: [$ \\succsim \\equiv (\\succsim_1, \\succsim_2, \\ldots, \\succsim_n) \\in \\mathscr{D}_I]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741b6",
      "text": "社会的選択対応とは非空対応 [$ F: \\mathscr{D}_I \\twoheadrightarrow X]のこと",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741b7",
      "text": "　ドメインから帰結への対応",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741b8",
      "text": "　「対応」[$ \\twoheadrightarrow]とは？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741b9",
      "text": " \t[$ F: X \\twoheadrightarrow Y]のとき[$ \\forall x \\in X, F(x) \\subset Y]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741ba",
      "text": " \t関数と比較してみよう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741bb",
      "text": "\t \t[$ f: X \\rightarrow Y]のとき[$ \\forall x \\in X, f(x) \\in Y]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741bc",
      "text": " \t[$ F, G : X \\twoheadrightarrow Y ] が[$ F \\subseteq G \\Leftrightarrow [F(x) \\subseteq G(x) \\forall x \\in X] ]のときFはGの「部分対応」と呼ぶ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741bd",
      "text": " \t[$ F : X \\twoheadrightarrow Y, f: X \\rightarrow Y ]が[$ f \\in F \\Leftrightarrow [f(x) \\in F(x) \\forall x \\in X] ]のときfはFの「セレクション」と呼ぶ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741be",
      "text": "　非空とは対応の終域が空でないということ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741bf",
      "text": "　　空だと「どの帰結もダメだ！」となるから都合が悪い、たぶん。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741c0",
      "text": "[社会的選択関数]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741c1",
      "text": "　社会的選択対応Fが常に一つの帰結を与える時、Fを[社会的選択関数]と呼び、fで表す。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741c2",
      "text": "　\t「社会的選択対応Fが常に一つの帰結を与える」とは[$ \\forall \\succsim \\in \\mathscr{D}_I, |F(\\succsim)| = 1]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741c3",
      "text": "[耐戦略性]([戦略的操作不可能性])",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741c4",
      "text": "\t[$ \\forall i\\in I, \\succsim \\in \\mathscr{D}_I, \\succsim_i' \\in \\mathscr{D}_i, f(\\succsim) \\succsim_i f(\\succsim_i', \\succsim_{-i})]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741c5",
      "text": "　つまりどのような選好組([$ \\succsim])においても、以下が成り立つ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1622179827
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741c6",
      "text": "　　誰か一人iの選好[$ \\succsim_i]を別の選好[$ \\succsim_i']に置き換えても、その結果得られる帰結[$ f(\\succsim_i', \\succsim_{-i})]は置き換えなかった場合に得られる帰結[$ f(\\succsim)]よりiに好まれることはない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741c7",
      "text": "　どの個人iにとっても、嘘をついて自分の本当の選好[$ \\succsim_i]以外の選好[$ \\succsim_i']を申告しても、自分にとってより好ましい帰結が得られることがない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    },
    {
      "id": "60ab9fa6aff09e00001741c8",
      "text": "　　だからみんな嘘をつかずに申告するよね、ということ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621860263,
      "updated": 1621860263
    }
  ]
}